768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/10-z16_Summit.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><h2><strong>實用</strong><strong>心意之選</strong><strong>| MSI Modern</strong><strong>系列，最低入手價只要</strong><strong>$4,799</strong></h2><p>若果想要拿出一個看起來體面又兼顧實用性的禮物，但又不想一次花大錢，MSI 的經典 Modern 系列手提電腦將會你的貼心禮物。MSI Modern 系列擁有時尚輕薄的外型，搭配不同的處理器，從 Intel Core i3 到 i7 應有盡有，讓你隨意根據自己的需求選擇最適合的電腦。</p><p><strong>Modern</strong><strong>系列，立即了解：<a href="https://hkstore.msi.com/pages/business-productivity-modern-series-notebook">按此</a></strong></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/09-Modern.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1077009" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/09-Modern-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/09-Modern-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/09-Modern-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/09-Modern-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/09-Modern.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><h2><strong>CP</strong><strong>值最高的打機首選</strong><strong>| MSI Katana GF/Sword</strong><strong>系列，最高慳</strong><strong>$3,300</strong></h2><p>如果你的朋友喜歡打機，就可在聖誕節考慮為他／她送上 MSI 熱賣的電競 Katana GF 與 Sword 系列。現在購買此系列電腦，最高可折$3,300。此價格實惠的打機神器，搭配 Intel Core i7 處理器與 GeForce RTX 30 系列顯示卡，可幫你這個聖誕贏下每一場 Game。</p><p>即日起到 12 月 31 日，MSI GF63 Thin 更有快閃優惠，價格最平至 $5,499，用家們不要錯過只有聖誕檔期的特別優惠了。</p><p><strong>Katana GF/Sword</strong><strong>系列</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>立即了解</strong><strong>：<a href="https://hkstore.msi.com/pages/msi-katana-gf-sword-series">按此</a></strong></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/04-katana.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1077010" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/04-katana-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/04-katana-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/04-katana-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/04-katana-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/04-katana.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/05-sword.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1077011" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/05-sword-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/05-sword-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/05-sword-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/05-sword-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/05-sword.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p>除了以上介紹的聖誕禮物清單，MSI 更準備了超多機種的限定優惠，讓大家有最豐富的選擇，更多聖誕折扣優惠詳情可看這裡：<a href="https://hkstore.msi.com/pages/2021xmas">按此</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
